                    <name type="place">Camden</name>
                    <date when="1886-09-07" rend="right">Sept: 7 p m</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener> 
            <p>I think every hour of the day, (&#38; night too when awake) of Hattie&#8212;&#38; of
                how it must be there with you &#38; Jess<ptr target="mhs.00022_n1"/>&#8212;but keep on much the same, with my
                doings &#38; affairs&#8212;</p><p>&#8212;I know well enough, dear brother, how gloomy &#38; blank
                all must be to you &#38; Jess.</p>
            <p>&#8212;I wish I could do something to help&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>W W</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="mhs.00022.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
